---
layout: base.njk
title: VPNHUB - Your Privacy, Protected
description: VPN tutorials, privacy guides, server tips, and video lessons.
---
<header class="hero privacy-hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <h1>Your Privacy, <span class="highlight">Protected</span></h1>
    <p>Discover the latest insights on digital privacy, security, and how VPNs are reshaping the way we browse the internet safely.</p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn" href="/tutorials/">Start Your Secure Journey</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section class="section feature-section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>Why Choose VPNHUB?</h2>
    <div class="grid features-grid">
      <div class="card feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">♢</div><h3>Military-Grade Encryption</h3><p>Learn practical privacy habits and secure VPN setup methods.</p></div>
      <div class="card feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">⚡</div><h3>Lightning Fast Speeds</h3><p>Follow simple guides for smooth, stable, and private browsing.</p></div>
      <div class="card feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">◎</div><h3>Global Server Network</h3><p>Understand servers, locations, protocols, and connection choices.</p></div>
      <div class="card feature-card"><div class="feature-icon">▢</div><h3>Zero-Log Policy</h3><p>Read beginner-friendly tutorials about privacy-first VPN use.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2>Latest Tutorials</h2>
    <p class="lead">Fresh guides and blog posts from VPNHUB.</p>
    <div class="grid">
      {% for post in collections.posts | reverse | slice(0, 6) %}
      <article class="post-card">
        {% if post.data.image %}<img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}">{% endif %}
        <div class="meta">{{ post.data.date }} · {{ post.data.category }}</div>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <a class="read-more" href="{{ post.url }}">Read More →</a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
